ub8e8\\uc5b4\\uc838 \\uc2e4\\uc2dc\\uac04 \\uc704\\ud5d8\\ubb3c \\uad00\\ub9ac\\uac00 \\uac00\\ub2a5\\ud574 \\uc11c\\uc6b8\\uc2dc \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc548\\uc804\\uacfc \\uc704\\uae30 \\ub300\\uc751\\ub825\\uc5d0 \\uae30\\ub300\\ub97c \\ubaa8\\uc73c\\uace0 \\uc788\\ub2e4.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\ubcf8 \\uc0ac\\uc5c5\\uc744 \\ub2f4\\ub2f9\\ud558\\uace0 \\uc788\\ub294 \\uc11c\\uc6b8\\uc2dc \\ub3c4\\ub85c\\uad00\\ub9ac\\uacfc \\ub2f4\\ub2f9 \\uc8fc\\ubb34\\uad00\\uc740 &ldquo;\\uc778\\uacf5\\uc9c0\\ub2a5 \\ubc0f \\ube45\\ub370\\uc774\\ud130 \\ub4f1\\uc758 \\ucca8\\ub2e8 \\uae30\\uc220\\uc744 \\uae30\\ubc18\\uc73c\\ub85c \\ubd88\\ud2b9\\uc815\\ud558\\uac8c \\ubc1c\\uc0dd\\ud558\\ub294 \\ud3ec\\ud2b8\\ud640\\uacfc \\uac19\\uc740 \\ub3c4\\ub85c\\uc704\\ud5d8\\uc815\\ubcf4\\ub97c \\uc2e4\\uc2dc\\uac04\\uc73c\\ub85c \\ud0d0\\uc9c0\\ud560 \\uc218 \\uc788\\ub2e4\\ub294 \\uac83\\uc740 \\ub3c4\\ub85c\\uad00\\ub9ac\\uc758 \\ud601\\uc2e0\\uc801\\uc778 \\uae30\\ud68c\\ub85c \\uc0dd\\uac01\\ud55c\\ub2e4&quot; \\uace0 \\uae30\\ub300\\uac10\\uc744 \\ub098\\ud0c0\\ub0c8\\ub2e4.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8\\uc758 \\uc815\\ub9cc\\uc2dd \\ub300\\ud45c\\ub294 &ldquo;\\uc774\\ubc88 \\uc0ac\\uc5c5\\uc218\\uc8fc\\ub97c \\uc758\\ubbf8 \\uc788\\uac8c \\uc0dd\\uac01\\ud558\\uba70, \\uc0ac\\uc5c5\\uc644\\ub8cc\\uae4c\\uc9c0 \\uc548\\uc815\\uc801\\uc778 \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4 \\uc9c0\\uc6d0\\uc744 \\uc704\\ud574 \\ub178\\ub825\\ud558\\uaca0\\uc73c\\uba70, \\uc774\\ubc88 AI \\ub2e8\\ub9d0\\uae30\\uc640 \\uc778\\uacf5\\uc9c0\\ub2a5 \\ud50c\\ub7ab\\ud3fc\\uc758 \\ubcf8\\uaca9\\uc801\\uc778 \\uc11c\\uc6b8 \\uad8c\\uc5ed \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4\\ub97c&nbsp; \\uc2dc\\uc791\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc804\\uad6d\\uc744 \\ucee4\\ubc84\\ud558\\ub294 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc548\\uc804\\ub9dd \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4\\ub85c \\uc131\\uc7a5\\uc744 \\uae30\\ub300\\ud558\\uace0 \\uc788\\ub2e4&quot; \\uace0 \\ub9d0\\ud588\\ub2e4.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}]}', '{\"en\":\"\",\"kr\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/02\\/26\\/smart-city2-m_65dc5938cfedc.jpg\"}', 5, 'kr', 'D', 'Y', 'Y', '2024-02-26', 4, 1, '2024-02-26 01:30:28', '2024-02-26 01:42:49'),
(13, 'Dareesofts RiaaS performance inspected by Seoul City Mayor Mr. Oh Se-hoon', 'dareesofts-riaas-performance-inspected-by-seoul-city-mayor-mr-oh-se-hoon', '[]', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft\'s RiaaS performance inspected by Seoul City Mayor Mr. Oh Se-hoon\",\"kr\":\"\"}', '{\"en\":\"Since July last year, the Seoul Metropolitan Government has been operating an \'AI Pothole Automatic Detection System\' provided by Dareesoft, that uses artificial intelligence (AI) to find and repair potholes. The Service is called RiaaS (Road Hazard Information as a Service).\",\"kr\":\"\"}', '{\"en\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>On this pleasant afternoon of March 14, 2024, as the weather gradually warms, the media is buzzing with news of Seoul Mayor, Mr. Oh Se Hoon, conducting an inspection of the Automatic AI Pothole Detection technology implemented by the Seoul government. Dareesoft takes pride in its role <strong>as the service provider of AI-based automatic pothole detection services to the Seoul Metropolitan City<\\/strong> since July of last year. The flagship Dareesoft&#39;s offering is RiaaS (Road Hazard Information as a Service), a flagship solution based service for automatic pothole detection utilizing AI-based camera technology. However, RiaaS extends beyond mere AI vision technology; it integrates IoT, connectivity, and big data, culminating in a comprehensive end to end service. RiaaS facilitates the real-time transmission of detected hazard information to stakeholders through data connections and cloud services. This groundbreaking technology has transformed road hazard maintenance in South Korea and particularly in Seoul which is one of the most advance smart cities in the world known for its pioneering advancements in smart infrastructure.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2023\\/12\\/26\\/ai-road-analyzer-01_658a9619546d0.jpg\",\"caption\":\"ARA (AI Road Analyzer Device)\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_1\",\"head\":\"Let\'s have a deeper look at how RiaaS works\",\"text\":\"<p>RiaaS largely has the following 3 components:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>1. An AI vision based, plug and play, edge device called ARA or AI Road Analyzer, equipped with state of the art dual camera, RTK GPS presicion, data connection and storage facilities.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2. A cloud service which does a second round of data cleansing and final data processing along with blurring of private information like people&#39;s face, number plates of the vehicles, deduplication of the data etc.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3. Monitoring Dashboard which presents the data in realtime to the stake holders with the image and exact location of the hazards.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>With the recent approval of Seoul city&#39;s Mayor Mr. Oh Se Hoon, Dareesoft is confident that our innovative solutions will continue to enhance the efficiency and safety of Seoul&#39;s road infrastructure, contributing to the city&#39;s reputation as a global leader in smart urban development.<\\/p>\"}],\"kr\":[]}', '{\"en\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/03\\/14\\/nisi20240314-0020265651-web_65f2b6196a935.jpg\",\"kr\":\"\"}', 404, 'en', 'A', 'Y', 'N', '2024-03-14', 4, 1, '2024-03-13 23:11:17', '2024-07-13 09:15:46'),
(14, 'Introducing RiaaS', 'introducing-riaas', '[]', '{\"en\":\"\",\"kr\":\"\\uc778\\uacf5\\uc9c0\\ub2a5 \\uae30\\ubc18 \\uc2e4\\uc2dc\\uac04 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc704\\ud5d8\\uc815\\ubcf4 \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4 - RiaaS\"}', '{\"en\":\"\",\"kr\":\"RiaaS\\ub97c \\uc560\\ub2c8\\uba54\\uc774\\uc158\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc27d\\uac8c \\uc54c\\uc544\\ubcf4\\uc138\\uc694.\"}', '{\"en\":[],\"kr\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p><strong>\\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc704\\ud5d8\\uc815\\ubcf4 \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4 Road Hazard Information as a Service : RiaaS&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><iframe allow=\\\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" referrerpolicy=\\\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/S_Gmxwzgwn4?si=XyFDzkjsMPw1N1Kj\\\" title=\\\"YouTube video player\\\" width=\\\"560\\\"><\\/iframe><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc704\\uc5d0 \\uc874\\uc7ac\\ud558\\ub294 \\uc218\\ub9ce\\uc740 \\uc704\\ud5d8\\uc694\\uc18c\\ub4e4, \\ube44\\uc640 \\uc790\\ub3d9\\ucc28 \\ud558\\uc911\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc778\\ud574 \\ubc1c\\uc0dd\\ud558\\ub294 \\ud3ec\\ud2b8\\ud640. \\ucc28\\ub7c9\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\ub5a8\\uc5b4\\uc9c0\\ub294 \\uac01\\uc885 \\ub099\\ud558\\ubb3c\\uacfc \\uc4f0\\ub808\\uae30\\ub4e4, \\ub3c4\\ub85c\\uac00 \\uac08\\ub77c\\uc838 \\ubc1c\\uc0dd\\ud558\\ub294 \\uac01\\uc885 \\uade0\\uc5f4 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc704\\uc5d0\\ub294 \\uc6b0\\ub9ac\\uac00 \\uc0dd\\uac01\\uc9c0\\ub3c4 \\ubabb\\ud558\\ub294 \\ub2e4\\uc591\\ud55c \\uc704\\ud5d8\\ubb3c\\uc774 \\uc874\\uc7ac\\ud569\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<br \\/>\\r\\n\\uc774\\ub7ec\\ud55c \\uc704\\ud5d8\\ubb3c\\ub4e4\\uc740 \\uc6b4\\uc804\\uc790\\ub4e4\\uc758 \\uc548\\uc804\\uc744 \\uc704\\ud611\\ud558\\uae30 \\ub54c\\ubb38\\uc5d0 \\ube60\\ub974\\uace0 \\uc815\\ud655\\ud55c \\ud0d0\\uc9c0\\ub97c \\ud1b5\\ud574, \\uc0ac\\uace0 \\ubc1c\\uc0dd \\uc774\\uc804 \\uc120\\uc81c\\uc801\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc870\\uce58\\ud574\\uc57c \\ud569\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\ub2e4\\uc591\\ud55c \\uc704\\ud5d8 \\uc694\\uc18c\\ub97c \\uc2e4\\uc2dc\\uac04\\uc73c\\ub85c \\ud0d0\\uc9c0\\ud558\\uae30 \\ud55c \\uc778\\uacf5\\uc9c0\\ub2a5, \\ube45\\ub7ec\\ub2dd \\uadf8\\ub9ac\\uace0 IoT \\uae30\\uc220 \\uae30\\ubc18\\uc758 \\uc194\\ub8e8\\uc158 <strong>RiaaS<\\/strong>\\ub97c \\uc9e7\\uc740 \\uc560\\ub2c8\\uba54\\uc774\\uc158\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc27d\\uace0 \\uac04\\ub2e8\\ud558\\uac8c \\uc54c\\uc544\\ubcf4\\uc2dc\\uae30 \\ubc14\\ub78d\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}]}', '{\"en\":\"\",\"kr\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/05\\/10\\/riaas-001_663daa419c1f1.png\"}', 27, 'kr', 'A', 'Y', 'Y', '2024-06-05', 2, 1, '2024-05-09 19:50:28', '2024-06-13 23:18:19'),
(15, 'Empowering Indonesias Road Management Dareesofts Journey to Safer Roads', 'empowering-indonesias-road-management-dareesofts-journey-to-safer-roads', '[]', '{\"en\":\"Empowering Indonesia\\u2019s Road Management: Dareesoft\\u2019s Journey to Safer Roads\",\"kr\":\"\\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uad00\\ub9ac \\uac15\\ud654: \\uc548\\uc804\\ud55c \\ub3c4\\ub85c\\ub97c \\uc704\\ud55c Dareesoft\\uc758 \\uc5ec\\uc815\"}', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft is making significant strides on the global stage with its commitment to enhancing road safety. Recently, the company showcased its innovative technology at the 2024 Korea Construction and Transport Technology Fair in Indonesia. Hosted by the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, and Transport Korea, and KAIA (Korea Agency for Infrastructure Technology Advancement), this event provided Dareesoft a platform to demonstrate how its technology can revolutionize road management by detecting hazards in real-time and digitizing crucial data for long-term budget planning.\",\"kr\":\"Dareesoft\\ub294 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc548\\uc804 \\uac15\\ud654\\ub97c \\ud5a5\\ud55c \\ud5cc\\uc2e0\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc138\\uacc4 \\ubb34\\ub300\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\ud070 \\uc9c4\\uc804\\uc744 \\uc774\\ub8e8\\uace0 \\uc788\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.\"}', '{\"en\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Dareesoft is making significant strides on the global stage with its commitment to enhancing road safety. Recently, the company showcased its innovative technology at the 2024 Korea Construction and Transport Technology Fair in Indonesia. Hosted by the Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, and Transport Korea, and KAIA (Korea Agency for Infrastructure Technology Advancement), this event provided Dareesoft a platform to demonstrate how its technology can revolutionize road management by detecting hazards in real-time and digitizing crucial data for long-term budget planning.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/2_6668ff48d72ca.jpg\",\"caption\":\"Indonesia\'s New Capital Smart City \'Nusantara\' Seminar\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>In a dynamic setting that included seminars on Indonesia&rsquo;s new Smart Capital City &lsquo;Nusantara&rsquo; and strategies for Korean companies navigating Indonesia&rsquo;s business landscape, Dareesoft excelled in the 1:1 Business Matching session. The company garnered significant interest from key players like PT Jasamarga Tollroad Maintenance and PT Astra Tol Nusantara, both giants in Indonesia&rsquo;s toll road maintenance sector. Their enthusiasm for Dareesoft&rsquo;s flagship service, RiaaS (Road Hazard Information as a Service), underscored the technology&#39;s potential to transform road maintenance practices in Indonesia.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/4_6668ff48d4a2c.jpg\",\"caption\":\"PT Astra Tol Nusantara 1:1 Meeting Session\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Dareesoft&rsquo;s impact extended beyond these sessions. Other Indonesian companies, recognizing the value of Dareesoft&rsquo;s technology, forged partnerships to introduce it to higher levels of government. CV. Wimeta, with its extensive experience in assessing road conditions in Kalimantan and Sumatera, signed an MOU with Dareesoft, signaling a collaborative effort to enhance road safety nationwide.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/6_6668ff48cb856.jpg\",\"caption\":\"MOU Ceremony with CV Wimeta\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Moreover, Korean companies with a strong presence in Indonesia expressed keen interest in Dareesoft&rsquo;s technology. Through strategic partnerships such as the Letter of Distribution signed with PT Smart Knowledge Indonesia, Dareesoft is poised to expand its reach across Java Island and beyond.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/7_6668ff48ccc75.jpg\",\"caption\":\"Company Visit to PT Smart Knowledge Indonesia\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/8_6668ff48c19e3.jpg\",\"caption\":\"1:1 Business Matching Meeting Preparation\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>This brief yet fruitful business trip to Indonesia reaffirmed Dareesoft&rsquo;s belief in the transformative power of RiaaS. As interest from Indonesian road maintenance authorities continues to grow, Dareesoft remains dedicated to promoting its technology worldwide. For Dareesoft, RiaaS is not just a solution&mdash;it&rsquo;s a revolution in road management.<\\/p>\"}],\"kr\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Dareesoft\\ub294 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc548\\uc804 \\uac15\\ud654\\ub97c \\ud5a5\\ud55c \\ud5cc\\uc2e0\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc138\\uacc4 \\ubb34\\ub300\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\ud070 \\uc9c4\\uc804\\uc744 \\uc774\\ub8e8\\uace0 \\uc788\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\ucd5c\\uadfc \\ud68c\\uc0ac\\ub294 \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uc5f4\\ub9b0 2024\\ub144 \\ud55c\\uad6d \\uac74\\uc124 \\ubc0f \\uad50\\ud1b5 \\uae30\\uc220 \\ubc15\\ub78c\\ud68c\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\ud601\\uc2e0\\uc801\\uc778 \\uae30\\uc220\\uc744 \\uc120\\ubcf4\\uc600\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\ud55c\\uad6d \\uad6d\\ud1a0\\uad50\\ud1b5\\ubd80\\uc640 \\ud55c\\uad6d\\uac74\\uc124\\uae30\\uc220\\uc5f0\\uad6c\\uc6d0\\uc774 \\uc8fc\\ucd5c\\ud55c \\uc774\\ubc88 \\ud589\\uc0ac\\uc5d0\\uc11c Dareesoft\\ub294 \\uc2e4\\uc2dc\\uac04\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uc704\\ud5d8\\uc744 \\uac10\\uc9c0\\ud558\\uace0 \\uc7a5\\uae30 \\uc608\\uc0b0 \\uacc4\\ud68d\\uc744 \\uc704\\ud55c \\uc911\\uc694\\ud55c \\ub370\\uc774\\ud130\\ub97c \\ub514\\uc9c0\\ud138\\ud654\\ud558\\uc5ec \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uad00\\ub9ac \\ubc29\\uc2dd\\uc744 \\ud601\\uc2e0\\ud560 \\uc218 \\uc788\\ub294 \\uae30\\uc220\\uc744 \\uc2dc\\uc5f0\\ud560 \\uae30\\ud68c\\ub97c \\uac00\\uc84c\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/2_6668ff48d72ca.jpg\",\"caption\":\"\\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544 \\uc2e0 \\uc2a4\\ub9c8\\ud2b8 \\uc218\\ub3c4 \'\\ub204\\uc0b0\\ud0c0\\ub77c\' \\uc138\\ubbf8\\ub098\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>\\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544\\uc758 \\uc0c8\\ub85c\\uc6b4 \\uc2a4\\ub9c8\\ud2b8 \\uc218\\ub3c4 &#39;\\ub204\\uc0b0\\ud0c0\\ub77c&#39;\\uc640 \\ud55c\\uad6d \\uae30\\uc5c5\\ub4e4\\uc774 \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544 \\uc0ac\\uc5c5 \\ud658\\uacbd\\uc744 \\ud0d0\\uc0c9\\ud558\\ub294 \\uc804\\ub7b5\\uc5d0 \\uad00\\ud55c \\uc138\\ubbf8\\ub098\\ub97c \\ud3ec\\ud568\\ud55c \\uc5ed\\ub3d9\\uc801\\uc778 \\uc124\\uc815\\uc5d0\\uc11c Dareesoft\\ub294 1:1 \\ube44\\uc988\\ub2c8\\uc2a4 \\ub9e4\\uce6d \\uc138\\uc158\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\ub450\\uac01\\uc744 \\ub098\\ud0c0\\ub0c8\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\ud68c\\uc0ac\\ub294 \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544\\uc758 \\uc720\\ub8cc \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc720\\uc9c0\\ubcf4\\uc218 \\ubd84\\uc57c\\uc758 \\uac70\\ub300 \\uae30\\uc5c5\\uc778 PT Jasamarga Tollroad Maintenance\\uc640 PT Astra Tol Nusantara\\uc640 \\uac19\\uc740 \\uc8fc\\uc694 \\uae30\\uc5c5\\ub4e4\\ub85c\\ubd80\\ud130 \\ud070 \\uad00\\uc2ec\\uc744 \\ubc1b\\uc558\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\uc774\\ub4e4\\uc758 Dareesoft\\uc758 \\ub300\\ud45c \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4\\uc778 RiaaS(\\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc704\\ud5d8 \\uc815\\ubcf4 \\uc11c\\ube44\\uc2a4)\\uc5d0 \\ub300\\ud55c \\uc5f4\\uc815\\uc740 \\uc774 \\uae30\\uc220\\uc774 \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544\\uc758 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc720\\uc9c0\\ubcf4\\uc218 \\uad00\\ud589\\uc744 \\ubcc0\\ud654\\uc2dc\\ud0ac \\uc7a0\\uc7ac\\ub825\\uc744 \\uac15\\uc870\\ud588\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/4_6668ff48d4a2c.jpg\",\"caption\":\"PT Astra Tol Nusantara\\uc640\\uc758 1:1 \\ubbf8\\ud305 \\uc138\\uc158\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Dareesoft\\uc758 \\uc601\\ud5a5\\ub825\\uc740 \\uc5ec\\uae30\\uc11c \\uadf8\\uce58\\uc9c0 \\uc54a\\uc558\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. Dareesoft\\uc758 \\uae30\\uc220 \\uac00\\uce58\\ub97c \\uc778\\uc815\\ud55c \\ub2e4\\ub978 \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544 \\uae30\\uc5c5\\ub4e4\\uc740 \\uc815\\ubd80\\uc758 \\ub354 \\ub192\\uc740 \\uc218\\uc900\\uc5d0 \\uc774\\ub97c \\uae30\\uc220\\uc744 \\ub3c4\\uc785\\ud558\\uae30 \\uc704\\ud574 \\ud30c\\ud2b8\\ub108\\uc2ed\\uc744 \\ub9fa\\uc5c8\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\uce7c\\ub9ac\\ub9cc\\ud0c4\\uacfc \\uc218\\ub9c8\\ud2b8\\ub77c\\uc758 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc0c1\\ud0dc \\ud3c9\\uac00\\uc5d0 \\uad11\\ubc94\\uc704\\ud55c \\uacbd\\ud5d8\\uc744 \\uac00\\uc9c4 CV. Wimeta\\ub294 Dareesoft\\uc640 \\uc591\\ud574\\uac01\\uc11c\\ub97c \\uccb4\\uacb0\\ud558\\uc5ec \\uc804\\uad6d\\uc801\\uc73c\\ub85c \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc548\\uc804\\uc744 \\ud5a5\\uc0c1\\uc2dc\\ud0a4\\uae30 \\uc704\\ud55c \\ud611\\ub825 \\ub178\\ub825\\uc744 \\uc2e0\\ud638\\ud588\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/6_6668ff48cb856.jpg\",\"caption\":\"CV Wimeta\\uc640 MOU \\uccb4\\uacb0\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>\\ub610\\ud55c, \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544\\uc5d0 \\uac15\\ub825\\ud55c \\uc785\\uc9c0\\ub97c \\uac00\\uc9c4 \\ud55c\\uad6d \\uae30\\uc5c5\\ub4e4\\uc740 Dareesoft\\uc758 \\uae30\\uc220\\uc5d0 \\ud070 \\uad00\\uc2ec\\uc744 \\ubcf4\\uc600\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. PT Smart Knowledge Indonesia\\uc640 \\uccb4\\uacb0\\ud55c \\ubc30\\uae09 \\uacc4\\uc57d\\uc11c\\ub97c \\ud1b5\\ud574 Dareesoft\\ub294 \\uc790\\ubc14 \\uc12c \\uc804\\uc5ed \\ubc0f \\uadf8 \\uc774\\uc0c1\\uc73c\\ub85c \\ud655\\uc7a5\\ud560 \\uc900\\ube44\\uac00 \\ub418\\uc5c8\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<\\/p>\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/7_6668ff48ccc75.jpg\",\"caption\":\"PT Smart Knowledge Indonesia \\ubc29\\ubb38\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_3\",\"image\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/8_6668ff48c19e3.jpg\",\"caption\":\"1:1 \\ube44\\uc988\\ub2c8\\uc2a4 \\ub9e4\\uce6d \\uc900\\ube44 \\ud604\\ud669\"},{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>\\uc774 \\uc9e7\\uc9c0\\ub9cc \\uacb0\\uc2e4\\uc744 \\ub9fa\\uc740 \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544 \\ucd9c\\uc7a5\\uc73c\\ub85c Dareesoft\\ub294 RiaaS\\uc758 \\ubcc0\\ud601\\uc801 \\ud798\\uc5d0 \\ub300\\ud55c \\uc2e0\\ub150\\uc744 \\uc7ac\\ud655\\uc778\\ud588\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. \\uc778\\ub3c4\\ub124\\uc2dc\\uc544 \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uc720\\uc9c0\\ubcf4\\uc218 \\ub2f9\\uad6d\\uc758 \\uad00\\uc2ec\\uc774 \\uacc4\\uc18d \\uc99d\\uac00\\ud568\\uc5d0 \\ub530\\ub77c, Dareesoft\\ub294 \\uc804 \\uc138\\uacc4\\uc801\\uc73c\\ub85c \\uae30\\uc220\\uc744 \\ud64d\\ubcf4\\ud558\\ub294 \\ub370 \\uc804\\ub150\\ud558\\uace0 \\uc788\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. Dareesoft\\uc5d0\\uac8c RiaaS\\ub294 \\ub2e8\\uc21c\\ud55c \\uc194\\ub8e8\\uc158\\uc774 \\uc544\\ub2c8\\ub77c \\ub3c4\\ub85c \\uad00\\ub9ac\\uc758 \\ud601\\uba85\\uc785\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.<\\/p>\"}]}', '{\"en\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/1_6668ff48dbf8f.jpg\",\"kr\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/06\\/12\\/1_6668ff48dbf8f.jpg\"}', 64, 'both', 'D', 'Y', 'N', '2024-06-12', 5, 1, '2024-06-11 16:54:40', '2024-06-25 23:13:59'),
