(4, 'Julia Fredenbug', 'fredenbug@protonmail.com', 'Afghanistan', 'Can you enhance your blog pages?', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nIs there any way that you can provide an audio version of your blog?\r\n\r\nI recently started commuting with my new job for few hours in the day driving and I would still like to read your new blogs.\r\n\r\nI\'ve a friend who told me that she added a button on her website that transforms the text into human like audio.\r\n\r\nYou can see the audio button on her website, like in this blog.\r\n\r\nhttps://media.ascensionpress.com/2019/08/01/want-a-deeper-surrender-let-it-go-with-this-novena/\r\n\r\nShe is using a service called websitevoice https://websitevoice.com/ and she says its free and easy to install.\r\n\r\nThe audio sounds great to me and I would appreciate if you can do the same, a male voice would be great in my opinion :)\r\n\r\nThanks\r\n\r\nJulia Fredenbug', '194.26.129.198', '2024-02-12 02:57:51', '2024-02-12 02:57:51', 'Julia'),
(5, '김유환', 'kyh79486@jbcorporation.com', '대한민국', '문의', '안녕하세요. \r\n충청권 도시가스 공급을 담당하고 있는 JB주식회사의 DT사업팀장 김유환이라 합니다. \r\n저희 팀도 AI 기반의 신규사업 업무를 수행하고 있고 관련 사업 검토 중 귀 사의 기술과 \r\n서비스 범위에 대해 높은 관심을 갖고 있습니다. \r\n괜찮으시면 격 없는 미팅을 통해 귀 사와의 협업 포인트가 있는지 모색해 보고 싶습니다.\r\n연락 주십시요. 감사합니다.', '121.184.223.200', '2024-03-20 01:30:34', '2024-03-20 01:30:34', 'JB주식회사'),
