(11, '구서정', 'sj9koo@gmail.com', '대한민국', 'ARA 20 카메라 구매 문의', '안녕하세요. 다라소프트의 도로분석 장치에 관심있어서 문의 드립니다.\r\nARA 20에 AI가 탑재되어 있다고 알고 있는데 혹시 AI탑재 안 된 카메라만 구매 가능 할까요? \r\n가능하다면 가격이 얼마인지 문의드리고 싶습니다.', '119.200.173.20', '2024-05-06 21:38:40', '2024-05-06 21:38:40', '지엔아이씨티'),
(12, 'Emily Stone', 'emily@wikismastery.com', 'United States', 'Get A Wikipedia Page For Yourself Or For Your Company.', 'Wikipedia is considered to be the World’s most significant tool for reference material. The Wiki links show up on the 1st page of Google 97% of the time. With a Page on one of the most revered reference tools, you are sure to get yourself or your business noticed. So if you\'re thinking of getting a Wikipedia Page created, it\'s the best time of the year.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in getting more information just respond back to this email.\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\n\r\nEmily Stone\r\nWiki Mastery\r\nemily@wikismastery.com\r\n\r\nRespond with stop to optout.', '111.88.229.63', '2024-05-28 10:08:57', '2024-05-28 10:08:57', 'Wiki Mastery'),
