(24, 'Dareesoft featured in KBS for RiaaS deployment in Hwaseong City', 'dareesoft-featured-in-kbs-for-riaas-deployment-in-hwaseong-city', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft featured in KBS for RiaaS deployment in Hwaseong City\",\"kr\":\"\"}', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft has been spotlighted on one of Korea\'s biggest news channels #KBS news for our groundbreaking efforts in tackling road hazards!\",\"kr\":\"\"}', '{\"en\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Dareesoft has been spotlighted on one of Korea&#39;s biggest news channels&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"0\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=kbs&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#KBS<\\/a>&nbsp;news for our groundbreaking efforts in tackling road hazards!<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nWith roads becoming increasingly perilous due to potholes and debris, Dareesoft&#39;s innovative solutions are making waves. Our cutting-edge digital system, recently adopted by Hwaseong City in Gyeonggi Province, is revolutionizing road maintenance.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nThrough the strategic deployment of ARA devices on public buses and taxis, coupled with advanced AI technology, we&#39;re swiftly identifying and categorizing road imperfections, from potholes to litter, enabling rapid response and efficient management.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nAccording to Kang Hyun-cheol, an official from Hwaseong City Development Corporation, &quot;We often encounter road hazards, especially potholes, during our operations. Thanks to Dareesoft&#39;s solution, we can now detect and address these issues in real-time.&quot;<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nMayor Jung Myeong-geun emphasized the city&#39;s commitment to enhancing this system, aiming to increase accuracy and response speed further. &quot;By expanding our fleet of camera-equipped vehicles and refining our automatic classification capabilities, we&#39;re poised to ensure safer roads for our citizens.&quot;<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nThis recognition from a prominent news outlet underscores Dareesoft&#39;s dedication to leveraging technology for the betterment of communities. Stay tuned as we continue to innovate and make strides in road safety across Korea and beyond! The news can be seen by visiting the link below.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>https:\\/\\/news.kbs.co.kr\\/news\\/pc\\/view\\/view.do?ncd=7883950<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\n<a data-attribute-index=\\\"1\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=dareesoft&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#Dareesoft<\\/a>&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"2\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=roadsafety&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#RoadSafety<\\/a>&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"3\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=innovation&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#Innovation<\\/a>&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"4\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=hwaseongcity&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#HwaseongCity<\\/a>&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"5\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=koreannewscoverage&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#KoreanNewsCoverage<\\/a>&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"6\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=aitechnology&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#AITechnology<\\/a>&nbsp;<a data-attribute-index=\\\"7\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/feed\\/hashtag\\/?keywords=communityimpact&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7160896449163980800\\\">#CommunityImpact<\\/a><\\/p>\"}],\"kr\":[]}', '{\"en\":\"uploads\\/2024\\/02\\/07\\/hwaseong-city-kbs_65c35c4c240d1.png\",\"kr\":\"\"}', 'news', 'en', 'A', 'Y', '2024-02-07', 1, '2024-02-07 10:34:09', '2024-02-07 10:35:21'),
