(33, 'Dareesoft displays RiaaS at the Good Roads Conference Toronto Canada', 'dareesoft-displays-riaas-at-the-good-roads-conference-toronto-canada', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft displays RiaaS at the Good Roads Conference Toronto Canada\",\"kr\":\"\\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8, Toronto Good Roads Conference & Trade Show \\ubd80\\uc2a4 \\ucc38\\uc5ec\"}', '{\"en\":\"RiaaS became major attraction at Good Roads Conference and Trade Show\",\"kr\":\"\\uce90\\ub098\\ub2e4 \\ud1a0\\ub860\\ud1a0\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uc5f4\\ub9b0 Good Roads Conference & Trade Show \\ubd80\\uc2a4\\uc5d0\\uc11c RiaaS\\uac00 \\uc131\\ud669\\ub9ac\\uc5d0 \\uc18c\\uac1c\\ub418\\uc5c8\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.\"}', '{\"en\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>After successful participations in the prestigious Intertraffic Amsterdam and the renowned NACE Annual Conference, Dareesoft is making its mark at another significant event, this time in Toronto! At Good Roads Conference and Trade Show Dareesoft engaged with the largest road networks globally, introduced ther expertise and solutions to the heart of Canada. The event is being attended by hundreds of government officials who are in-charges of Candian Roads and Bridges at various levels and departments.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nAt Booth 107 Dareesoft exchanges ideas, explores potential collaborations, and together, paves the way for a brighter, more efficient future for road infrastructure.<\\/p>\"}],\"kr\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>\\uc62c\\ud574, \\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8\\ub294 \\ub2e4\\uc591\\ud55c \\ud574\\uc678 \\uc804\\uc2dc\\ud68c \\ucc38\\uc5ec\\ub97c \\ud1b5\\ud574 \\uc138\\uacc4\\ub85c \\ubed7\\uc5b4\\ub098\\uac08 \\ud1a0\\ub300\\ub97c \\ub9c8\\ub828\\ud558\\uace0 \\uc788\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.&nbsp;<br \\/>\\r\\nIntertraffic Amsterdam, NACE Annual Conference\\uc5d0 \\uc774\\uc5b4, \\uc9c0\\ub09c 4\\uc6d4 21\\uc77c\\ubd80\\ud130 24\\uc77c\\uae4c\\uc9c0 \\uce90\\ub098\\ub2e4 \\ud1a0\\ub860\\ud1a0\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uc5f4