(34, 'Dareesoft Exhibits at Intertraffic Amsterdam', 'dareesoft-exhibits-at-intertraffic-amsterdam', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft Registers its Presence in Intertraffic Amsterdam\",\"kr\":\"\\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8, \\uae00\\ub85c\\ubc8c \\uad50\\ud1b5 \\uae30\\uc220 \\uc804\\uc2dc\\ud68c Intertraffic Amsterdam 2024 \\ucc38\\uc5ec\"}', '{\"en\":\"Crowd of smart city consultants and private players appreciated RiaaS\",\"kr\":\"\\ub124\\ub35c\\ub780\\ub4dc \\uc554\\uc2a4\\ud14c\\ub974\\ub2f4\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uac1c\\ucd5c\\ub41c Itertraffic Amsterdam 2024\\uc5d0 \\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8\\uac00 \\ud568\\uaed8\\ud588\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4.\"}', '{\"en\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>RiaaS is being liked at Intertraffic Amsterdam, happening from April 16th to 19th, 2024!<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nJoin Dareesoft at Booth \\ud835\\udfce\\ud835\\udfd6.\\ud835\\udfd3\\ud835\\udfd4\\ud835\\udfd3\\ud835\\udc00 and embark on a journey into the future of mobility and traffic technology! Experience firsthand our cutting-edge AI Technology for Road Maintenance, revolutionizing how we monitor and manage road conditions. From real-time hazard detection to proactive maintenance solutions, Dareesoft is leading the charge towards safer and smarter infrastructure.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nRiaaS is being appreciated by government officials, road construction and safety companies.<\\/p>\"}],\"kr\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>\\uc9c0\\ub09c 4\\uc6d4 16\\uc77c\\ubd80\\ud130 19\\uc77c\\uae4c\\uc9c0, \\ub124\\ub35c\\ub780\\ub4dc \\uc554\\uc2a4\\ud14c\\ub974\\ub2f4\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uac1c\\ucd5c\\ub41c <strong>Itertraffic Amsterdam 2024<\\/strong>\\uc5d0 \\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8\\uac00 \\ud568\\uaed8\\ud588\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\ub2e4. &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Intertraffic Amsterdam\\uc740 1972\\ub144\\ubd80\\ud130 \\uc774\\uc5b4\\uc9c4 \\uc138\\uacc4\\uc801\\uc778 \\uaddc\\ubaa8\\uc758 \\uae00\\ub85c\\ubc8c \\uad50\\ud1b5 \\uae30\\uc220 \\uc804\\uc2dc\\