(35, 'Dareesoft making waves at NACE conference 2024 in Riverside County', 'dareesoft-making-waves-at-nace-conference-2024-in-riverside-county', '{\"en\":\"Dareesoft is making waves at NACE conference 2024 in Riverside County\",\"kr\":\"\\uce98\\ub9ac\\ud3ec\\ub2c8\\uc544 NACE \\ucee8\\ud37c\\ub7f0\\uc2a4\\uc5d0 \\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8 \\ucc38\\uc5ec\"}', '{\"en\":\"RiaaS became the point of attraction to the visitors and exhibitors\",\"kr\":\"\\ubbf8\\uad6d \\uce98\\ub9ac\\ud3ec\\ub2c8\\uc544\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uac1c\\ucd5c\\ub41c NACE Annual Conference \\ucc38\\uc5ec \\uc18c\\uc2dd\\uc744 \\ud655\\uc778\\ud558\\uc138\\uc694.\"}', '{\"en\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>Dareesoft is making waves at The National Association of County Engineers Annual Conference! Join Dareesoft at the Palm Springs Convention Center in Riverside County from April 15th to 18th, where innovation meets excellence. Dareesoft is proud to be exhibiting our groundbreaking RIAAS (Road Hazard information as a Service) at Booth No. 7! Get ready to witness firsthand how RIAAS is revolutionizing the road maintenance landscape with cutting-edge technology and unparalleled expertise.<br \\/>\\r\\n<br \\/>\\r\\nDon&#39;t miss this golden opportunity to connect with Dareesoft CEO Betty Row and North America General Sales Manager Douglas Dragovich, explore cutting-edge solutions, and discover the future of infrastructure management with Dareesoft! See you there!<br \\/>\\r\\n&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}],\"kr\":[{\"layout\":\"layout_2\",\"text\":\"<p>4\\uc6d4 15\\uc77c\\ubd80\\ud130 18\\uc77c\\uae4c\\uc9c0, \\uce98\\ub9ac\\ud3ec\\ub2c8\\uc544\\uc758 \\ub9ac\\ubc84\\uc0ac\\uc774\\ub4dc \\uce74\\uc6b4\\ud2f0 \\ud31c\\uc2a4\\ud2b8\\ub9ac\\uc2a4 \\ucee8\\ubca4\\uc158 \\uc13c\\ud130\\uc5d0\\uc11c \\uac1c\\ucd5c\\ub41c <strong>NACE(The National Association of County Engineers) \\ucee8\\ud37c\\ub7f0\\uc2a4<\\/strong>\\uc5d0 \\ub2e4\\ub9ac\\uc18c\\ud504\\ud2b8\\uac00 \\ud568\\uaed8\\ud588\\uc2b5\\ub2c8\\